{"id": "art-66", "label": "Art. 66", "title": "Art. 66: Abţinerea", "slug": "art-66", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1196156035\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2704\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1196156035\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 66:\nAb&#355;inerea </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1310294426\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2703\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1310294426\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Persoana incompatibil&#259; este obligat&#259; s&#259;\ndeclare, dup&#259; caz, pre&#351;edintelui instan&#355;ei, procurorului care\nsupravegheaz&#259; urm&#259;rirea penal&#259; sau procurorului ierarhic\nsuperior c&#259; se ab&#355;ine de a participa la procesul penal, cu\nar&#259;tarea cazului de incompatibilitate &#351;i a temeiurilor de fapt care\nconstituie motivul ab&#355;inerii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1124216817\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2702\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1124216817\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Declara&#355;ia de ab&#355;inere se face de îndat&#259;\nce persoana obligat&#259; la aceasta a luat cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259; de\nexisten&#355;a cazului de incompatibilitate.</span></p>"}